
Christopher Mitchell released a  comprehensive report on publicly owned networks throughout the USA: “[http://www.muninetworks.org/reports/breaking-broadband-monopoly Breaking the Broadband Monopoly]]” explains how public ownership of networks differs from private, evaluates existing publicly owned networks, details the obstacles to public ownership, offers lessons learned, and wrestles with the appeal and difficulty of the open access approach.

